{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be user-friendly and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Sterling Legal Group</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #2a4f98; /* A professional blue */\n            --secondary-color: #5d80b1; /* A lighter shade of blue */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --footer-background: #f4f7fc;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin: 0.5rem 0 0;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 0.8rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #e0e0e0;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            padding: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        #about p {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n\n        .services-list {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .services-list li {\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .services-list li:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .services-list h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        #contact form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        #contact input,\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 80%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #cccccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        #contact textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        #contact button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-background);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Sterling Legal Group</h1>\n        <p>Your Trusted Partners in Legal Excellence</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Sterling Legal Group</h2>\n            <p>\n                At Sterling Legal Group, we are dedicated to providing comprehensive and strategic legal solutions.\n                Our team of experienced attorneys is committed to upholding the highest standards of integrity,\n                professionalism, and client advocacy. We strive to build lasting relationships based on trust and\n                mutual respect, ensuring your legal needs are met with precision and care.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <ul class=\"services-list\">\n                <li>\n                    <h3>Corporate Law</h3>\n                    <p>Navigating complex business transactions and regulatory compliance.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                    <h3>Real Estate Law</h3>\n                    <p>Expert guidance for all your property-related legal matters.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                    <h3>Litigation</h3>\n                    <p>Aggressive representation in civil and commercial disputes.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                    <h3>Family Law</h3>\n                    <p>Compassionate support for sensitive family legal issues.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                    <h3>Intellectual Property</h3>\n                    <p>Protecting your innovations and creative works.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                    <h3>Estate Planning</h3>\n                    <p>Securing your legacy for future generations.</p>\n                </li>\n            </ul>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form>\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Sterling Legal Group. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>123 Law Lane, Suite 400, Metropolis, CA 90210 | (555) 123-4567</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic form submission simulation\n        document.querySelector('#contact form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault(); // Prevent actual form submission\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch shortly.');\n            this.reset(); // Clear the form\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}